InfoWorld這裡列出2015年度最佳雲端/資料中心的開源系統軟體開源系統軟體是造就雲端風潮的技術根本。回想起十年前，大家開始喊雲端，有多少人意識到這件事? 記得當年一大堆人在做雲端的研發，不知道發展出那些好用的東西?很多人把「系統」看得太小了，可能與電子業的思維有關。其實「系統」談的是如何把多個組件整合在一起的科學和技術。資訊科技，不只讓單一電腦的能力越來越強大，更重要的是讓由眾多電腦所組成的系統更為強大。懂得系統，會知道這類問題的複雜性和難度，因此需要更多元的系統軟體。到了今天，傳統的「系統軟體」「作業系統」課程中教的東西，只是基礎。在實務上，當前的重點在於由多台電腦所組成的複雜系統，而一個厲害的「系統架構師」（System Architect），必須知道如何綜合使用好用的系統軟體，來輔助規劃、營運、管理、分析複雜的系統。這些好用的系統軟體，有時間多學一個，功力就多一分；學會如何綜合運用，境界就提升一級；懂得修改這些開源計畫來滿足應用需求，就能夠解決許多問題；有能力改良創新這些開源計畫，那就是炙手可熱的人物。Docker Machine, Compose, and Swarm - Container.CoreOS and Rkt - a thin, lightweight server OS, CoreOS is based on Google’s Chromium OS.RancherOS - a minimal OS suitable for hosting container-based applications in cloud infrastructures.Kubernetes - a container orchestration system designed to manage and run applications built in Docker and Rocket containers.Apache Mesos - manage thousands of servers, using containers to host applications and APIs to support parallel application development.Joyent’s SmartOS/SmartDataCenter - a thin server OS and its management platform.Sensu - monitor servers, services, application health, and business KPIs.Prometheus - a service monitoring system designed to deliver alerts to operators.Elasticsearch - scalable search across a mix of content types, including structured and unstructured documents.Ansible - a minimal management service, using SSH to manage Unix nodes and PowerShell to work with Windows servers, with no need to deploy agentsJenkins - a cross-platform, continuous integration and continuous delivery application that increases your productivity.Node.js - an asynchronous event driven framework for building scalable network applications.Seneca - a microservices toolkit for Node.js, which helps to write clean, organized code..Net - Microsoft’s open-sourcing of .NetGluster - aggregate various storage servers into one large parallel network file system.
